addr-type.help: IP version to use for IP packets.
addr-type.name: addr-type

options.help: Use IPv4 addressing for IP packets.
Use IPv6 addressing for IP packets.

auth-alg.help: Authentication algorithm. Must be the same for both ends of the tunnel.
auth-alg.name: auth-alg

auth-key.help: Hexadecimal authentication key in 16-digit (8-byte) segments separated by hyphens.
auth-key.name: auth-key

enc-alg.help: Encryption algorithm. Must be the same for both ends of the tunnel.
enc-alg.name: enc-alg

enc-key.help: Hexadecimal encryption key in 16-digit (8-byte) segments separated by hyphens.
enc-key.name: enc-key

interface.help: Name of the physical, aggregate, or VLAN interface.
interface.name: interface

ip-version.help: IP version to use for VPN interface.
ip-version.name: ip-version

local-gw.help: IPv4 address of the local gateway's external interface.
local-gw.name: local-gw

local-gw6.help: Local IPv6 address of VPN gateway.
local-gw6.name: local-gw6

local-spi.help: Local SPI, a hexadecimal 8-digit (4-byte) tag. Discerns between two traffic streams with different encryption rules.
local-spi.name: local-spi

remote-gw.help: IPv4 address of the remote gateway's external interface.
remote-gw.name: remote-gw

remote-gw6.help: Remote IPv6 address of VPN gateway.
remote-gw6.name: remote-gw6

remote-spi.help: Remote SPI, a hexadecimal 8-digit (4-byte) tag. Discerns between two traffic streams with different encryption rules.
remote-spi.name: remote-spi
